history.content:
We are currently seeking students to serve as a Reader and grade work for the course this semester. 
Requirements:
  1. Must be registered at UC Berkeley this semester.
  2. Overall GPA of 3.0 or higher, and maintain this GPA during the semester you are teaching
  3. Have previously taken the course, its equivalent or a more advanced course, with a grade of B or better
If you are interested and available 9 to 20 hours per week (probably through finals week?), please email me and copy Professor Wu (wu@eecs.berkeley.edu)
history.subject: Seeking Paid EE 105 Reader for remainder of semester
